 {"id":"bd-yx9r.10.2","title":"Implement web router, middleware, extract, session, static, SSE, multipart, and security parity","description":"The upstream web layer is extensive and user-facing. ANSI C needs comparable routing/middleware/handler/extract/session/static/SSE/multipart/request-region/security/debug/Next.js bootstrap surfaces or it should stop claiming crate-level parity.","design":"Port the web stack in layered form, with strong request-lifecycle diagnostics and operator-friendly logs for routing, auth failures, stream responses, and static file/service behavior.","acceptance_criteria":"A. Public web modules cover the major upstream families with explicit lifecycle/security semantics.\\nB. Tests cover routing, extraction failures, session/security behavior, streaming responses, and multipart/static handling.\\nC. Logged web e2e scenarios exist for representative browser/client/server flows.","notes":"Depends on H1 plus C1/C2/C3.","status":"open","priority":1,"issue_type":"task","created_at":"2026-03-13T20:38:42.100031287Z","created_by":"ubuntu","updated_at":"2026-03-13T22:27:24.992394011Z","source_repo":".","compaction_level":0,"original_size":0,"labels":["crate-parity","web"],"dependencies":[{"issue_id":"bd-yx9r.10.2","depends_on_id":"bd-yx9r.1","type":"blocks","created_at":"2026-03-13T22:27:22.987790348Z","created_by":"ubuntu","metadata":"{}","thread_id":""},{"issue_id":"bd-yx9r.10.2","depends_on_id":"bd-yx9r.10","type":"parent-child","created_at":"2026-03-13T20:38:42.100031287Z","created_by":"ubuntu","metadata":"{}","thread_id":""},{"issue_id":"bd-yx9r.10.2","depends_on_id":"bd-yx9r.10.1","type":"blocks","created_at":"2026-03-13T20:39:47.693136553Z","created_by":"ubuntu","metadata":"{}","thread_id":""},{"issue_id":"bd-yx9r.10.2","depends_on_id":"bd-yx9r.2","type":"blocks","created_at":"2026-03-13T22:27:23.987519648Z","created_by":"ubuntu","metadata":"{}","thread_id":""},{"issue_id":"bd-yx9r.10.2","depends_on_id":"bd-yx9r.3","type":"blocks","created_