-{"id":"bd-yx9r.8","title":"Network core parity beyond minimal net stubs","description":"The Rust crate exports a substantial networking surface (, , , , , , plus reactor integration). The ANSI C tree currently has only minimal net ghosts and cannot honestly claim comparable networking capability.","design":"This epic should build the real network substrate that later TLS, HTTP, gRPC, database, messaging, and distributed work can sit on.","acceptance_criteria":"A. ANSI C gains substantive networking modules beyond placeholder wrappers.\\nB. Native and deterministic/lab test lanes cover connection lifecycle, resolution, socket errors, and platform-gated behavior.\\nC. Later protocol stacks can depend on this substrate instead of bespoke scaffolding.","notes":"Primary upstream references: src/net/*, io-related exports in src/lib.rs, and src/runtime/reactor/*.","status":"open","priority":0,"issue_type":"epic","created_at":"2026-03-13T20:38:32.579614341Z","created_by":"ubuntu","updated_at":"2026-03-13T22:29:49.481203170Z","source_repo":".","compaction_level":0,"original_size":0,"labels":["crate-parity","io","network"],"dependencies":[{"issue_id":"bd-yx9r.8","depends_on_id":"bd-yx9r","type":"parent-child","created_at":"2026-03-13T20:38:32.579614341Z","created_by":"ubuntu","metadata":"{}","thread_id":""},{"issue_id":"bd-yx9r.8","depends_on_id":"bd-yx9r.1","type":"blocks","created_at":"2026-03-13T20:39:08.448184036Z","created_by":"ubuntu","metadata":"{}","thread_id":""},{"issue_id":"bd-yx9r.8","depends_on_id":"bd-yx9r.2","type":"blocks","created_at":"2026-03-13T20:39:09.467045678Z","created_by":"ubuntu","metadata":"{}","thread_id":""},{"issue_id":"bd-yx9r.8","depends_on_id":"bd-yx9r.3","type":"blocks","created_at":"2026-03-13T20:39:10.495164372Z","created_by":"ubuntu","metadata":"{}","thread_id":""},{"issue_id":"bd-yx9r.8","depends_on_id":"bd-yx9r.7","type":"blocks","created_at":"2026-03-13T22:29:49.480542931Z","created_by":"ubuntu","metadata":"{}","thread_id":""}]}
