-{"id":"bd-yx9r.8.2","title":"Implement Unix-domain, ancillary-data, and split-stream parity","description":"Upstream networking also includes Unix sockets, ancillary data, and split-stream helpers that matter for native deployments and inter-process coordination. ANSI C lacks these public surfaces today.","design":"Port these as explicit native-only modules with fail-closed behavior on unsupported profiles and with careful attention to ownership and descriptor lifecycle.","acceptance_criteria":"A. Public Unix/ancillary/split APIs exist for supported profiles with clear exclusions elsewhere.\\nB. Tests cover socket lifecycle, ancillary payload handling, split semantics, and unsupported-profile errors.\\nC. Native smoke scenarios generate detailed logs/artifacts for success and failure cases.","notes":"Depends on D1 and F1.","status":"open","priority":1,"issue_type":"task","created_at":"2026-03-13T20:38:35.163090138Z","created_by":"ubuntu","updated_at":"2026-03-13T22:29:50.743641543Z","source_repo":".","compaction_level":0,"original_size":0,"labels":["crate-parity","net","unix"],"dependencies":[{"issue_id":"bd-yx9r.8.2","depends_on_id":"bd-yx9r.1","type":"blocks","created_at":"2026-03-13T22:27:14.281243261Z","created_by":"ubuntu","metadata":"{}","thread_id":""},{"issue_id":"bd-yx9r.8.2","depends_on_id":"bd-yx9r.2","type":"blocks","created_at":"2026-03-13T22:27:15.242655402Z","created_by":"ubuntu","metadata":"{}","thread_id":""},{"issue_id":"bd-yx9r.8.2","depends_on_id":"bd-yx9r.3","type":"blocks","created_at":"2026-03-13T22:27:16.173931189Z","created_by":"ubuntu","metadata":"{}","thread_id":""},{"issue_id":"bd-yx9r.8.2","depends_on_id":"bd-yx9r.6.1","type":"blocks","created_at":"2026-03-13T20:39:39.841582147Z","created_by":"ubuntu","metadata":"{}","thread_id":""},{"issue_id":"bd-yx9r.8.2","depends_on_id":"bd-yx9r.7","type":"blocks","created_at":"2026-03-13T22:29:50.742925829Z","created_by":"ubuntu","metadata":"{}","thread_id":""},{"issue_id":"bd-yx9r.8.2","depends_on