-{"id":"bd-yx9r.9","title":"Advanced transport and protocol substrate parity","description":"The Rust crate includes major advanced transport substrates still missing in ANSI C: TLS, WebSocket, QUIC (core and native), and server connection/shutdown layers. These are not optional if the goal is full crate-level functional parity.","design":"This epic should establish the secure and modern transport foundations used by HTTP, gRPC, web, and distributed/client stacks.","acceptance_criteria":"A. ANSI C exposes substantive TLS/WebSocket/QUIC/server substrates or explicit staged exclusions with diagnostics.\\nB. Tests and smoke packs cover handshake, stream lifecycle, error paths, and shutdown/replay artifacts.\\nC. The work composes with the service/transport and network-core layers rather than bypassing them.","notes":"Primary upstream references: src/tls/*, src/net/websocket/*, src/net/quic*/*, and src/server/*.","status":"open","priority":1,"issue_type":"epic","created_at":"2026-03-13T20:38:36.503398674Z","created_by":"ubuntu","updated_at":"2026-03-13T22:29:52.722826926Z","source_repo":".","compaction_level":0,"original_size":0,"labels":["crate-parity","quic","server","tls","websocket"],"dependencies":[{"issue_id":"bd-yx9r.9","depends_on_id":"bd-yx9r","type":"parent-child","created_at":"2026-03-13T20:38:36.503398674Z","created_by":"ubuntu","metadata":"{}","thread_id":""},{"issue_id":"bd-yx9r.9","depends_on_id":"bd-yx9r.1","type":"blocks","created_at":"2026-03-13T20:39:11.531631340Z","created_by":"ubuntu","metadata":"{}","thread_id":""},{"issue_id":"bd-yx9r.9","depends_on_id":"bd-yx9r.2","type":"blocks","created_at":"2026-03-13T20:39:12.589641Z","created_by":"ubuntu","metadata":"{}","thread_id":""},{"issue_id":"bd-yx9r.9","depends_on_id":"bd-yx9r.3","type":"blocks","created_at":"2026-03-13T20:39:13.629955115Z","created_by":"ubuntu","metadata":"{}","thread_id":""},{"issue_id":"bd-yx9r.9","depends_on_id":"bd-yx9r.6.3","type":"blocks","created_at":"2026-03-13T22:29:52.7221